---
title: HelloHero: All-American Crumbed Chicken with Parmesan, Roast Pumpkin & Apple Slaw
description: This crumb is like a bond between star-crossed lovers - unbeatable. It helps to keep those golden and crunchy breadcrumbs on the chicken so you get all the flavours in one bite. The only thing that could come close to beating them is a smokey aioli for dipping.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
